content: It is a waste of your money, don't bother yourself to download it. Very minimal drug list with no added value!
Very handy as quick reference for checking drug compatibility. I hope this gets updated frequently/as necessary.
App needs lot more drugs to be added currently it is half of time doesn't come up with information needed.
You can only use meds on their list. You can't type what you want in.
replyContent: Hi Angie, thanks for your review. The app description clearly states "This application provides the healthcare profession with a method of quickly checking the compatibility of any two of the following intravenous drugs at the Y-site:" and then goes on to list the 49 intravenous drugs that can be checked in the app. The app works as advertised.
